<chapter id="hudson-gadgets">
	<title>Hudson Gadgets</title>
	<para>
		This plugin includes several gadgets that can be displayed on the <trademark class="registered">Jira</trademark>
		dashboard or any other <trademark class="registered">Atlassian</trademark> product that can display gadgets, like
		<trademark class="registered">Confluence</trademark> or even non Atlassian products like iGoogle.
	</para>
	<para>
		The following sections detail the gadgets that are supported and the data that they display from Hudson.
		<note>
			<para>
				The sections detailing the gadgets assume that there is atleast one project on Hudson. The
				figures below use the builds of this plugin that is available on
				<ulink url="http://hudson.builds.marvelution.com">Marvelution's Hudson</ulink> instance.
			</para>
		</note>
	</para>
</chapter>
